values: This is the funniest thing ever. I haven't updated on livejournal in so long. But, this is the thing that has inspired me to update: Livejournal said this to me: Error * Please confirm you are a human below.

I tryed sleeping and unexpectantly couldn't. I felt so effing tired only an hour ago. Eh. I hate myself for this. I wanted to sleep!

I LOVE this bright eyes song : "Sor/Blue Angels Air Show". I guess there are two different titles. I don't know. I have "Sor" on my Itunes and I also have "Blue Angels Air Show" and they're exactly the same, so...

"so i am reminded of things ive forgotten.
the way doors can open and people just walk in.
its not unexpected, no its just how you planned it.
im beginning to think that it might never happen.
but now it is happening.

...

so we've been selected in this beautiful lottery.
we struggled so long but it ended so easy.
its starting to surface, all golden and godlike
this feeling we had every day and every night.
it bursts in an energy. a door it is opening."

This is a home-written story.




There once was boy name Mykell Anusny Giglioso. He became lost in the woods without anything, not even a watch. He knew he was late for dinner though, very late.


"Help me! Help me!" he yelled. Eventually he became so bored, he amused himself by waving his hand around. It was fun for a couple minutes, then he remembered how lost he was.


All of a sudden, a girl appeared! "I'm going to kill you," she said casually.


"What!" he exclaimed, "please don't."


Just in time, Capton Cannibis flew down from the trees to help Mykell.


He leaped down and tryed to help Mykell, but the girl beat him.


The girl brought Capton Cannibis to her friend's house to take care of him.


They raped him...


And then hung him.


Mykell was forced to watch the superhero die in a breathing struggle. It saddened him ever so.


Capton Cannibis was near his death, when he lept off into thin air in escape.


He flew off into the sky and lived. The girls tryed to find him, but never did.

THE END
